name: SPM5
body:
### Welcome to the SPM5 ongoing maintenance project
SPM5 is not maintained by its [original authors](http://www.fil.ion.ucl.ac.uk/spm/software/spm5/) anymore. This project attempts to maintain SPM5 sources so that they keep working with newer versions of Matlab.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
